dataLineage.statement:
Layer was downloaded as a shapefile by ITOS from a Dropbox link provided by the IMO. It was then analyzed by ITOS for errors. Those errors were corrected and the layer was sent back to UNOCHA as a feature class within a file geodatabase.
The following errors were found and fixed by ITOS: 1. Projection changed to "GCS_WGS_1984" 2. Created and populated Admin0 name and p-code fields 3. Removed Admin1 fields 4. Created and populated reference name field 5. The 5 records in the original layer were merged into 1 record 6. Fixed nesting errors with Admin0-2
